MORNING REPORT: PEOPLE WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By GREG BRAXTON, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Kid's All Right: New Kids on the Block member Donnie Wahlberg is scheduled 
to rejoin the group on its tour Thursday, four days after falling on stage and 
injuring himself during a concert. Wahlberg was released Tuesday from Saratoga 
Hospital after being treated for cuts and bruises on his chest and mouth. The 
New Kids revamped their concerts Tuesday and today in Auburn Hills, Mich.. GREG 
BRAXTON 
</P>
