RACIAL RELATIONS -- SOUTH AFRICA; SOUTH AFRICA -- GOVERNMENT; UNITED STATES -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SOUTH AFRICA; UNITED STATES -- POLITICS 
</P>
