<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB; 
</P>
<P>
MAN VS. MICROCHIP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I've been coming close on my triples lately, so I figure I'm due to hit. 
</P>
<P>
For today, my bets are $10 triples from Pendleton Ridge and High Rank in the 
fourth to Naturally Mitch in the fifth to Number's Game, Spirited Susan and 
Prosperity Road in the sixth. 
</P>
