</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA062790-0077 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 239412 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 27, 1990, Wednesday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 7B; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
