DRILLING -- UNITED STATES; OIL DRILLING -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; GOVERNMENT 
REGULATION; BUSH, GEORGE; LEASES; COASTAL AREAS -- UNITED STATES; COASTAL AREAS 
-- CALIFORNIA; OFFSHORE EXPLORATION; EXPLORATION OF RESOURCES 
</P>
