<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. STOCK WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Of the 100 largest publicly traded companies in Orange County, 26 gained value 
Tuesday, 38 lost and 36 remained unchanged for the day. 
</P>
